This is a perl script to show the rowcount and size of a table in Postgres.

Requirements: DBI, DBD::Pg


Usage: pg_rowcount.pl <database> <schema>

Output:
Table                                Rows                 Size
--------------------------------------------------------------
pg_statistic                         1853              1672 kB
pg_type                               910               168 kB
pg_attribute                         9569              1488 kB
pg_class                             1371               416 kB
pg_authid                              52                16 kB
pg_index                              766               112 kB
pg_operator                           705               104 kB
pg_database                            44                16 kB
[...] 
